<span id="freeTextContainer2104763412110462690">A sweet love story between a wounded single Mother and a confirmed bachelor. Abused by her first husband, Charlotte is wary of falling in love again. Jason is sure he will never get married. Charlotte’s teen age daughter tries to pay him to take her Mom out on a date but fate has a hand and they fall in love in their own. Easy read, sweet story.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


